sentences: Rydah J. Klyde is a Bay Area rapper from Pittsburg, California best known for his affiliation with the rap group Mob Figaz.
Around 2002, Rydah signed a solo deal with Mac Dre's Thizz Entertainment label.
In 2003, he released his album Tha Fly Gangsta.

In addition to releasing many songs on numerous Thizz compilations, Rydah saw the release of three albums; the first was an album with friend Johnny Cash as the group Money Gang titled Bang fo Bread, another solo album titled What's Really Thizzin?
and another group effort with Thizz affiliate Freako titled El Pueblo Children.
In 2006, the Money Gang released a mixtape titled 2 Chain Gang Vol. 1.
